                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-1560" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT MOORE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable V</hi> 12.) In consequence of information, I took the prisoner into custody, searched him, and found on him these taps, this bell-crank, and several small pieces of iron, which are here.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431023-name-1561" type="witnessName">
